{"search_data": "Central Pradhan Mantri Jan Aushadhi Yojana to be Launched in a MonthJan Aushadhi stores can be opened by NGO\u2019s, charitable institutions, reputed professional organizations, private hospitals and self help groups for the distribution of the medicines at affordable cost. The budget outlay for Jan Aushadhi Stores is Rs. 35 Crore.The Government is planning to increase to more than 500 from 361 medicines which were identified to be covered under the current Jan Aushadhi scheme. However, the scheme was able to cover only 130 of the 361 identified drugs.So far, about 157 Jan Aushadhi stores have been opened in states like Delhi, Uttarakhand, Odisha, Andhra Pradesh, Rajasthan, West Bengal, Jammu and Kashmir, Punjab, Haryana, Himachal Pradesh and Jharkhand.The operating agency which plans to open a Jan Aushadhi Store will be given a one-time assistance of Rs. 2 lakh as establishment cost. The government will also additionally assist the operating agency by Rs. 50 thousand as the startup cost.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}